      "para_id": "Q009241.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šu-Suen , the beloved of Enlil , the king whom Enlil chose with the love of his heart , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , presented this ( bowl ) to Abi-simti , his beloved mother ."
    }
